NEWS

Oct  8 2004	Updated the FAQ to include a paragraph on color banding
		issues and gamma correction. Thanks to Eric Rucker
		<bhtooefr@gmail.com> for bringing this issue to my attention.
		If you have this problem, look into the FAQ, it explains how
		this is caused and what to do about it.		

Sep 26 2004	Wrote a little FAQ document. I hope that it answers the most
		frequently asked questions and if actually helpful.

Sep  7 2004	min12xxw now uses autoconf to adapt to different OSs and
		machines. It does also include replacements for getline
		getopt_long library functions. Please note that you have
		to configure min12xxw now before you can build it.
